<subSubSection id="A8D0653DFF96FFF05889FBF1FD456487" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="E07536B6FF96FFF05889FBF1FD456487" blockId="91.[151,1437,1112,1535]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92">
This family of acalyptrate flies contains more than 800 species (
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05B72FBF1FBC465EF" author="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T." box="[876,1143,1148,1175]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" refId="ref350035" refString="Evenhuis, N. L. &amp; Pape, T. (2020) Systema Dipterorum. Version 2. 7. Available from: http: // www. diptera. org / (accessed 30 August 2020)" type="url" year="2020">Evenhuis &amp; Pape 2020</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05C94FBF1FAF065EF" author="Rondani, C." box="[1162,1347,1148,1174]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="32 - 46" refId="ref367046" refString="Rondani, C. (1843 d) Quattro specie di insetti ditteri proposti come tipi di generi nuovi. Memoria sesta per servire alla ditterologia italiana. Nuovi Annali delle Scienze Naturali, 10, 32 - 46, pl. I." type="journal article" year="1843">Rondani (1843d</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05D51FBF1FA2B65EE" author="Rondani, C." box="[1359,1432,1148,1175]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="1 - 10" refId="ref367399" refString="Rondani, C. (1845 b) Genera italica Conopidarum distincta et descripta. Fragmentum decimum tertium ad inserviendum dipterologiae italicae. Magasin de Zoologie d'Anatomie Comparee et de Palaeontologie, Series 2, 153, 1 - 10." type="journal article" year="1845">1845b</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05889FB2DFF6D65C2" author="Rondani, C." box="[151,222,1184,1211]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="165 - 197" refId="ref368231" refString="Rondani, C. (1850 c) Osservazioni sopra alquante specie di esapodi ditteri del Museo Torinese. Nuovi Annali delle Scienze Naturali e Rendiconto delle Sessioni della Societa Agraria e dell'Accademia delle Scienze dell'Istituto di Bologna, Series 3, 2, 165 - 197, 1 pl." type="journal article" year="1850">
1850 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF058CCFB2DFF6D65C2" author="Rondani, C." box="[210,222,1184,1211]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" refId="ref368338" refString="Rondani, C. (1856) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: I. Genera italica ordinis dipterorum ordinatim disposita et distincta et in familias et stirpes aggregata. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 226 pp. + [2] pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1856">c</bibRefCitation>
</bibRefCitation>
, 1856, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05933FB2DFEDB65C2" author="Rondani, C." box="[301,360,1184,1211]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" refId="ref368401" refString="Rondani, C. (1857) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: II. Species italicae ordinis dipterorum in genera characteribus definita, ordinatim collectae, methodo analitica distinctae, et novis vel minus cognitis descriptis. Pars prima. Oestridae: Syrphfidae [sic!]: Conopidae. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 264 pp., 1 pl. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1857">1857</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF0596FFB2DFE1F65C3" author="Rondani, C." box="[369,428,1184,1210]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" refId="ref369190" refString="Rondani, C. (1863) Diptera exotica revisa et annotata novis nonnullis descriptis. Eredi Soliani, Modena, 99 pp., 1 pl. [This is the separate that came out before the journal version with a different title, here as Rondani (1864 a)]." type="book" year="1863">1863</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF059A8FB2DFE4E65C2" author="Rondani, C." box="[438,509,1184,1211]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="127 - 146" refId="ref369345" refString="Rondani, C. (1865 a) Diptera italica non vel minus cognita descripta vel annotata observationibus nonnullis additis. Fasc. I. Oestridae - Syrphidae - Conopidae. Atti della Societa Italiana di Scienze Naturali, 8, 127 - 146." type="journal article" year="1865">1865a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05A19FB2DFDFD65C3" author="Rondani, C." box="[519,590,1184,1210]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="21 - 54" refId="ref369753" refString="Rondani, C. (1868 a) Diptera italica non vel minus cognita descripta vel annotata observationibus nonnullis additis. Fasc. III. Atti della Societa Italiana di Scienze Naturali, 11, 21 - 54." type="journal article" year="1868">1868a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05A46FB2DFD2C65C3" author="Rondani, C." box="[600,671,1184,1210]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="282 - 294" refId="ref370595" refString="Rondani, C. (1873 e) Muscaria exotica Musei Civici Januensis observata et distincta. Fragmentum I. Species aliquae in Abyssinia (Regione Bogos) lectae a Doct. O. Beccari et March. O. Antinori, anno 1870 - 71. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova, 4, 282 - 294. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. part. 9095" type="journal article" year="1873">1873e</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05AB7FB2DFD5C65C3" author="Rondani, C." box="[681,751,1184,1210]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="209 - 232" refId="ref370740" refString="Rondani, C. (1874 a) Degli insetti nocivi e dei loro parassiti. Enumerazione con note [Part]. Bullettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 5 (4) [1873], 209 - 232." type="journal article" year="1874">1874a</bibRefCitation>
) described 21 Palaearctic, one Neotropical and one Afrotropical nominal species. Eight of these are currently considered as valid, 13 as junior synonyms and two as doubtful (
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05D6BFB49FE96647B" author="Papavero, N." pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="1 - 28" refId="ref362528" refString="Papavero, N. (1971) Family Conopidae. In: Papavero, N. (Ed.), A catalogue of the Diptera of the Americas south of the United States. Museu de Zoologia, Universidade de Sao Paulo, Sao Paulo, 47, 1 - 28." type="journal article" year="1971">Papavero 1971</bibRefCitation>
, Smith 1980, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF059DCFB65FD08647B" author="Chvala, M. &amp; Smith, K. G. V." box="[450,699,1256,1282]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" refId="ref347709" refString="Chvala, M. &amp; Smith, K. G. V. (1988) Family Conopidae. In: Soos, A. &amp; Papp, L. (Eds.), Catalogue of Palaearctic Diptera. Volume 8. Syrphidae - Conopidae. Elsevier Science Publishers, Amsterdam &amp; Akademiai Kiado, Budapest, pp. 245 - 272." type="book" year="1988">Chv√°la &amp; Smith 1988</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05AD8FB65FBFB647A" author="Rivosecchi, L. &amp; Scaramozzino, P. L." box="[710,1096,1256,1283]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="1 - 4" refId="ref365822" refString="Rivosecchi, L. &amp; Scaramozzino, P. L. (1995) Diptera Conopoidea. In: Minelli, A., Ruffo, S. &amp; La Posta, S. (Eds.), Checklist delle specie della fauna italiana. 71. Calderini, Bologna, pp. 1 - 4." type="book chapter" year="1995">Rivosecchi &amp; Scaramozzino 1995</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05C4DFB65FAD7647B" author="Rivosecchi, L. &amp; Mei, M." box="[1107,1380,1256,1282]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="271 - 277" refId="ref365784" refString="Rivosecchi, L. &amp; Mei, M. (1998) Note sinonimiche su alcuni Conopidi descritti da Camillo Rondani (Diptera Conopidae). Fragmenta Entomologica, 30 (2), 271 - 277." type="journal article" year="1998">Rivosecchi &amp; Mei 1998</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05D71FB65FE8B645F" author="Mei, M. &amp; Stuke, J. - H." pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="3 - 10" refId="ref359176" refString="Mei, M. &amp; Stuke, J. - H. (2008) Remarks on Zodion nigritarsis (Strobl, 1902) and other European species of Zodion Latreille, 1796, with a revised key (Diptera, Conopidae). Tijdschrift voor Entomologie, 151, 3 - 10. https: // doi. org / 10.1163 / 22119434 - 900000247" type="journal article" year="2008">Mei &amp; Stuke 2008</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF0595AFA81FE75645F" author="Stuke, J. - H." box="[324,454,1292,1318]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="521 - 534" refId="ref376007" refString="Stuke, J. - H. (2016) Taxonomic notes on Western Palaearctic Conopidae (Diptera). Zootaxa, 4178 (4), 521 - 534. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4178.4.4" type="journal article" year="2016">Stuke 2016</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF059CCFA81FDBC645F" author="Stuke, J. - H." box="[466,527,1292,1318]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" refId="ref376050" refString="Stuke, J. - H. (2017) World catalogue of insects. Volume 15. Conopidae (Dipter a). Brill, Leiden, 354 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.1163 / 9789004271845" type="book" year="2017">2017</bibRefCitation>
). Rondani proposed three new substitute names for species previously described and named by other authors and also proposed a new name as a synonym not made available by use as a valid species before 1961 (
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05940FAD9FDB36416" author="Rondani, C." box="[350,512,1364,1391]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" refId="ref368401" refString="Rondani, C. (1857) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: II. Species italicae ordinis dipterorum in genera characteribus definita, ordinatim collectae, methodo analitica distinctae, et novis vel minus cognitis descriptis. Pars prima. Oestridae: Syrphfidae [sic!]: Conopidae. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 264 pp., 1 pl. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1857">Rondani 1857</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05A15FAD9FDE76417" author="Rondani, C." box="[523,596,1364,1390]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="209 - 232" refId="ref370740" refString="Rondani, C. (1874 a) Degli insetti nocivi e dei loro parassiti. Enumerazione con note [Part]. Bullettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 5 (4) [1873], 209 - 232." type="journal article" year="1874">1874a</bibRefCitation>
). 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05A79FAD9FC366417" author="Rivosecchi, L. &amp; Mei, M." box="[615,901,1364,1390]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" pagination="271 - 277" refId="ref365784" refString="Rivosecchi, L. &amp; Mei, M. (1998) Note sinonimiche su alcuni Conopidi descritti da Camillo Rondani (Diptera Conopidae). Fragmenta Entomologica, 30 (2), 271 - 277." type="journal article" year="1998">Rivosecchi &amp; Mei (1998)</bibRefCitation>
designated a 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF96FFF05C03FAD9FB376417" box="[1053,1156,1364,1390]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92">lectotype</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF96FFF05CACFAD9FEA364EA" authority="Rondani, 1865" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1865" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Sicus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="femoralis">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF96FFF05CACFAD9FAED6417" box="[1202,1374,1364,1390]" italics="true" pageId="91" pageNumber="92">Sicus femoralis</emphasis>
Rondani, 1865
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF96FFF05905FAF5FD6964EA" authority="Rondani, 1865" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1865" box="[283,730,1400,1427]" genus="Sphixosoma" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" rank="species" species="punctitarsis">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF96FFF05905FAF5FD9D64EB" box="[283,558,1400,1426]" italics="true" pageId="91" pageNumber="92">Sphixosoma punctitarsis</emphasis>
Rondani, 1865
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF96FFF05B0EFAF5FB6164EA" authority="Rondani, 1857" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1857" box="[784,1234,1400,1427]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Spixosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aureifasciata">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF96FFF05B0EFAF5FB9064EB" box="[784,1059,1400,1426]" italics="true" pageId="91" pageNumber="92">Spixosoma aureifasciata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05C34FAF5FB6164EA" author="Rondani, C." box="[1066,1234,1400,1427]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" refId="ref368401" refString="Rondani, C. (1857) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: II. Species italicae ordinis dipterorum in genera characteribus definita, ordinatim collectae, methodo analitica distinctae, et novis vel minus cognitis descriptis. Pars prima. Oestridae: Syrphfidae [sic!]: Conopidae. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 264 pp., 1 pl. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1857">Rondani, 1857</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, all of them in the MZUF. Here, we designate a 
<typeStatus id="3F718814FF96FFF059C5FA11FDF164CF" box="[475,578,1436,1462]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92">lectotype</typeStatus>
for 
<taxonomicName id="27CA4D35FF96FFF05A70FA10FC7C64CE" authority="Rondani, 1857" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1857" box="[622,975,1436,1463]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Myopa" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="punctum">
<emphasis id="D2BEEAA4FF96FFF05A70FA10FC9164CF" box="[622,802,1437,1462]" italics="true" pageId="91" pageNumber="92">Myopa punctum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FF96FFF05B36FA11FC7C64CE" author="Rondani, C." box="[808,975,1436,1463]" pageId="91" pageNumber="92" refId="ref368401" refString="Rondani, C. (1857) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: II. Species italicae ordinis dipterorum in genera characteribus definita, ordinatim collectae, methodo analitica distinctae, et novis vel minus cognitis descriptis. Pars prima. Oestridae: Syrphfidae [sic!]: Conopidae. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 264 pp., 1 pl. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1857">Rondani, 1857</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
. The type material has been recovered for all nominal species and is distributed among the MZUF (17), MSNC (four), OUMNH (three), MRSN (one), MSNG (one), MSNPV (one), MZUB (one) and MZUN (one).
</paragraph>
